== KeyCloakTokenExchangeResponseModel
:description: Java Web Token model. Retrieved from KeyCloak server via a token-exchange. Called from Future function link:copyAccessTokenToKeyCloak 

{description}

== Json Model
This returns a json model

== KeyCloakTokenExchangeResponseModel
[source,javascript]
----
  KeyCloakTokenExchangeResponseModel({
    required this.accessToken,
    required this.expiresIn,
    required this.refreshExpiresIn,
    required this.refreshToken,
    required this.tokenType,
    required this.notBeforePolicy,
    required this.sessionState,
    required this.scope,

  });
----
